Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ligamentous lesion' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Ligament of the femoral head' radio button is enabled
And 'Iliofemoral ligament' radio button is enabled
And 'Pubofemoral ligament' radio button is enabled
And 'Ischiofemoral ligament' radio button is enabled
And 'Transverse acetabular ligament' radio button is enabled

And 'Complete rupture' radio button is enabled
And 'Partial rupture' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Partial rupture' radio button
Then 'Thickening' checkbox is enabled
And 'T2w signal elevation' checkbox is enabled
